        "from": "T06n0220_315:0609c21_60",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以四念住性空，空中無趣無不趣故。",
        "from": "T06n0220_315:0609c21_61",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四正斷、四神足、五根、五力、七等覺支、八聖道支亦非趣非不趣。",
        "from": "T06n0220_315:0609c22_62",
