        "from": "T06n0220_315:0609c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以四正斷乃至八聖道支性空，空中無趣無不趣故。",
        "from": "T06n0220_315:0609c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「為諸有情宣說開示空解脫門非趣非不趣。",
        "from": "T06n0220_315:0609c25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
